8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Blackbox AI and Devin share a solid foundation of core features including Code Generation, Multi Language, Chat. Where Blackbox AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Autocomplete and Ide Integration, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Devin uniquely offers Code Review and Debugging and Refactoring and Test Generation and Documentation, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Blackbox AI holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Devin scores 7/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Blackbox AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $0, compared to Devin's starting price of $500/mo. Blackbox AI has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Devin does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
